(48, 22, 'en', 'AONANG PARADISE RESORT&LONGSTAY', 'aonang-paradise-resort-amp-longstay', 'Aonang paradise resort - Krabi Hotel Thailand is located a mere 400 metres from Aonang beach which can be easily reached with a 5 minute walk.', '<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size: x-large;">&nbsp;Aonang paradise resort</span></span></strong><span class="apple-converted-space"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span>- Krabi Hotel Thailand is located a mere 400 metres from Aonang beach which can be easily reached with a 5 minute walk</span><span lang="TH">ใ</span><span>Aonang Paradise Resort-Krabi stands out from other Aonang hotels due to it''s stylish combination of tropical lifestyle and contemporary design set amidst striking natural surroundings.&nbsp;A slice of tranquility, paradise offers privacy and intimacy under the shade of a wide variety of indigenous trees and shrubs which we have cultivated over the past decade.&nbsp;With over 10 years of experience in the Krabi hotels industry we strive to provide a uniquely friendly and informal service which we hope will put you at ease and make your stay at Aonang paradise a memorable one.&nbsp;This sophisticated provincial Krabi resort is an ideal location to spend a peaceful holiday.Our management''s no.1 commitment is to ensure service of the highest standards amongst Aonang hotels.&nbsp;Aonang Paradise Resort&hellip;&hellip;the one of the best destination of Krabi hotels.An ideal location to spend a peaceful holiday and relax, enjoyable for the whole family</span></p>', '<table border="1">\n<tbody>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td colspan="2">\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: xx-large;">Facilities&amp;Services</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>airport transfer</li>\n<li>business center</li>\n<li>coffee shop</li>\n<li>laundry service/dry cleaning</li>\n<li>poolside bar</li>\n<li>restaurant</li>\n<li>room srvice</li>\