(12, 2, 'en', 'Bhukitta Hotel & Spa', 'bhukitta-hotel-amp-spa', 'Bhukitta Hotel & spa is located in the heart of Phuket City which is easy to access “Old Town” and many attractions area', '<p><span>Bhukitta Hotel &amp; spa is located in the heart of Phuket City which is easy to access &ldquo;</span><strong>Old Town</strong>&rdquo; and many attractions area. The design of the Hotel combines an elegant blend of contemporary design with a modern Thai touch, all the latest amenities and free internet Wi-Fi, so ensuring a relaxing stay for all quests. Surest that everyday of your stay, indulge yourself with finest cuisine and exotic aromatherapy spa. Memorable getaways are guaranteed.</p>', '<table border="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2">\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;">Facilities</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="width: 300px;">\n<p><strong>Service &amp; Facilities Information:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>24 Hour Reception</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>24 Hour Security</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Airport Transfer</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Concierge Counter</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Bhukitta Spa and Sauna room</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Parking Area</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Complimentary Newpaper (Lobby Lounge)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Currency Exchange</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Free Internet Wi-Fi</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Laundry &amp; Dry Service</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Room Service (06.00 am. - 12.00 pm.)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Tours &amp; Transport Desk</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Meeting Room</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Swimming Pool</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bar:</strong></p>\n<p>Food lover can fully enjoy an extensive range of local dishes in a wide variety of regional styles: Thai &amp; international food, Barbecue Seafood Dinner. Discover a wonderful place to sit and enjoy to fresh seafood and relaxing drinks in the evening.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Pop Up Restaurant &amp; Bar 5.00 p.m. - 01.00 a.m.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Bhukitta Restau