(182, 'en', 'Laguna Phuket Golf Club', 'laguna-phuket-golf-club', 'You can enjoy the tranquility of a tropical island setting the challenge of a world-class,award winning golf course.', '<p><span id="internal-source-marker_0.6747096289040201">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;At <span style="font-size: x-large; color: #ff9900;"><span style="font-size: xx-large;">L</span>aguna Phuket Golf Club</span>, you can enjoy the tranquility of a tropical island setting the challenge of a world-class,award winning golf course,and the superb facilities within Laguna Phuket Resort-Asia''s first fully integrated resort development.</span></p>', '<table style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; height: 75px; width: 363px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;" rowspan="2">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Glof Course</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;" colspan="4">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Other Fee</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Caddy</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Club set</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Shoes</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Umbella</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">9 Holes</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">300</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">1,000/1,200</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">200</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style