(180, 'en', ' Blue Canyon Country Club - Lakes Course', 'blue-canyon-country-club-lakes-course', 'The course is a mixture of water-filled canyons created by open cast mining with its natural land flow left relatively unchanged.', '<p><span id="internal-source-marker_0.7279941612516994">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color: #ff9900; font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: xx-large;">T</span>he course is a mixture of water-filled canyons</span> created by open cast mining with its natural land flow left relatively unchanged. Its front 9 holes run through a landscape of lakes and original canyons, whilst the back 9 weaves around more scenic lakes and soft whispering woodlands of rubber trees. The Lakes Course distinctly features one of the largest green in this part of the world to test the putting skills of all golfers.</span></p>', '<div align="center">\n<table style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; height: 44px; width: 443px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="width: 100px; border: 1px solid #ffff99;" rowspan="2">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Glof Course</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 525px;" colspan="4">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Other Fees</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="width: 75px; border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Caddy</p>\n</td>\n<td style="width: 300px; border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Club set</p>\n</td>\n<td style="width: 75px; border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Shoes</p>\n</td>\n<td style="width: 120px; border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Club car</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="width: 100px; border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">18&nbsp;Holes</p>\n</td>\n<td style="wid