(178, 'en', 'Blue Canyon Country Club - Canyon Course', 'blue-canyon-country-club-canyon-course', 'Located on 720 acres (1,800 rai) of prime land, The blue Canyon Country Club is recognized as the most exclusive golfing establishment in the region.', '<p><span id="internal-source-marker_0.8760212287118079">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: xx-large;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #ff9900;"><span style="font-size: xx-large;">L</span>ocated on 720 acres </span></span><span style="color: #ff9900;">(1,800 rai) of prime land,</span> The blue Canyon Country Club is recognized as the most exclusive golfing establishment in the region. Developed in 1988, Blue Canyon Country Club from an old tin mine and rubber plantations,with both the golf course molded around the existing rubber plantations to ensure minimal disruption to the surrounding natural landscape. Cradled in a verdant valley against a magnificent backdrop of the majestic Phang Nga Mountains and Andaman. Blue Canyon Country Club offers two award winning 18-hole championship golf courses.</span></p>', '<div align="center">\n<table style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; height: 53px; width: 430px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;" rowspan="2">\n<p style="text-align: center;">Glof Course</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;" colspan="4">\n<p style="text-align: center;">Other Fees</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Caddy</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Club set</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Shoes</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center">Club car</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n