ree</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', '<ul>\n<li>\n<p>05.30 &ndash; 06.30 am. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pick up from hotel.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>08.30 am. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Arrive at Taplamu pier (tea,coffee served)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>08.45 am. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Depart from Taplamu pier to Similan islands by speed boat.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>10.10 am. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Arrive in Similan islands (divemaster will pick you up from speed boat to Similan Pro Dive&rsquo;s boat).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>10.45 am. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;First dive (1).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>12.00 am. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Lunch served on board.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>13.15 pm. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Second dive (2).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>15.00 pm. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Return by speed boat and depart from Similan islands.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>16.30 pm. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Arrive at Taplamu pier.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>19.30 pm. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Arrive at hotel.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>', '<p>Every Wednesdat and sunday will diving at Ball Island (2 time) and Ta chai Island ( 2 time )</p>\n<p>not included</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Equipment for the dive.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Towel</p>\n</li>\n</ul>', '2013-02-18 16:13:42', NULL, '2013-02-18 16:13:42', NULL, 385),
(147, 'en', 'Bamboo&Yao Yai Island', 'bamboo-amp-yao-yai-island', 'Enjoyment with diving canoe boat and tour nature in Bamboo-Yao Yai Island.', '<p>Tour Concept : Escape from the crowded tourists&sbquo;plus Yao yai Island.<br />Islands to visit : Plus private beach &amp; Beach BBQ and self paddle canoe.</p>', '<table border="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="border-style: solid; border-color: #ffff99; width: 120px; text-align: center;">\n<p><span style="font-size: x-large; color: #000000;">Time</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style="border-style: solid; border-color: #ffff99; text-align: center;">\n<p><span style="font-size: x-large; color: #000000;">Detail</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>07.45-08.00</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Pick up time from hotel to Port Island Hopper - Koh Sirae.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>08.00-08.30</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>30 &ndash; 45 minutes arrive to Port-welcome by your Local guide.<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Welcome with Cofee,tea,local pineapple biscuits.<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Re Infomation of tour program,weather in fact,accepted by customers</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>08.45-09.30</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>40 minutes explore to Bamboo Island, arrive at the paradise beach and amazing the turquized blue sea color.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>09.30-12.30</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Free style swimming,snorkelling,relaxing and enjoy walking around Bamboo Island and visit Fishing cottages.<br />* We serv with soft drinks,drinking water,seasonal fruits and some local snacks on the Island.<br />* During the times relax on Island , &nbsp;to deeper snorkelling area at " Hin Klang Reefs&rdquo; &nbsp;,will be appointed with the local guide.( in case of good weather &nbsp;condition .)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>12.30-14.00</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>20 minutes by speedboat to Yao Yai Island,<br /> welcome buffet Lunch in front of our private beach restaurant and free BeachBBQ.Seafood.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>14.00-14.30</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Relax after lunch.<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Free beach chair and umbrella. &nbsp;&nbsp; <br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Free self paddle canoe , beach games , bicycle</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>14.30-15.30</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Free &nbsp;local fancy bus inside Yao Yai Island :<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;visit and learn the culture &nbsp;such as ;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- General view of rice field,water buffalos and Thai Farmers . &nbsp;&nbsp;<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Picture of southern Thai House<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Fisherman way Picture of fishing &nbsp;nests, dry fishes &amp; squids products<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;along the way .<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Coconut Trees with the famous " Thai Makak Monkeys "<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Home stayed &nbsp;- &nbsp;Life style included &nbsp;garden of herbal ,fruits , &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;vegetables and animals .<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- Rubber Plantation - inspection &nbsp;how to cut off the liquid from the trees &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and using machine.<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- School inspection - local students ( except Saturday,Sunday or school &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;holidays )</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>15.30-16.00</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Back to our private beach - free style on the beach.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>16.00-16.30</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Back to Port Island Hopper. &nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 120px;">\n<p>16.30-17.00</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Arrive at Hotel by pleasant trip</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', '<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Chair and umbrella for relax on the beach</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Equipment for diving</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Breakfast and Lunch (Buffet)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Canoe boat</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Snack Tea Coffee</p>\n</li>\n</ul>', '', '2013-02-19 10:13:16', NULL, '2013-02-19 10:13:16', NULL, 389);
