(188, 'en', 'Package 3days 2nights Half Day Koh Khai – Phuket City Tour – Phang nga Bay', 'package-3days-2nights-half-day-koh-khai-ndash-phuket-city-tour-ndash-phang-nga-bay', 'Package 3days 2nights Half Day Koh Khai – Phuket City Tour – Phang nga Bay bring you to the island. ', '<div>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="color: #ff9900;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: xx-large;">P</span>ackage 3 days 2 nights</span> Half Day Koh Khai &ndash; Phuket City Tour &ndash; Phang nga Bay bring you to the island.</span> Diving at Khai island and Phang-nga bay. Watch the show at <span style="color: #ff9900;">Phuket Fantasea</span>. Travel at Phuket town for see the old building style chinoprotugish, view on Khaorang and worship venerable monk Champ at Chalong temple.</p>\n</div>', '<p><strong>Day1</strong>: Phuket Airport &ndash; Hotel &ndash; Khai Island Half Day</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Arrival to Phuket Airport and transfer to your hotel (Flight recommend to arrive before 10.00 hrs)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Approx 12.30 hrs. driver will pick you up at hotel lobby to the pier.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Depart from the pier to <span style="color: #ff9900;">Khai Island.</span><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Arrive<span style="color: #ff9900;"> Khai Nai</span> for snorkeling and relaxing on the white beach.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Depart to Khai Nui for snorkeling and swimming.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Visit <span style="color: #ff9900;">Khai Nok</span> for snorkeling, feeding foods for plenty of colorful fishes. Enjoy swimming and snorkeling at the crystal clear sea water.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Depart Khai Island back to the pier and further transfer to your hotel.</p>\n<p><strong>Day2</strong>: Phuket City Tour</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Approx 14.00 hrs, Driver will pick&nbsp; you up at hotel lobby for Phuket City Tour.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Visit the <span style="color: #ff9900;">Sino Portuguese House</span> in Downtown of Phuket City.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Visit the hill top of Rang Hill where the scenic of Phuket Town.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Visit the largest and most famous temple of Phuket, Chalong Temple.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Visit the<span style="color: #ff9900;"> viewpoint of Kata</span>, <span style="color: #ff9900;">Karon</span> before going to see the sunset at Phomtep Camp.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Transfer back to your hotel.</p>\n<p><strong>Day3</strong>: Day Trip to Phang Nga Bay</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;After your Breakfast, ready to check out and store your luggage at hotel lobby. Driver will pick you up for Phang Nga Trip (pick up time to be confirmed.)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Depart to Phang nga by air-condition minibus. Arrive at Phang nga bay to take long tail boat through the mangrove forest. Visit <span style="color: #ff9900;">James Bond Island</span> (Khao Tapoo) where the movie &ldquo; <span style="color: #ff9900;">The man with golden gun</span>&rdquo; was produce film. Visit <span style="color: #ff9900;">Khao Ping Kan</span>, <span style="color: #ff9900;">Tham Lod</span> (Grotto Cave) &nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Lunch at Panyee Island, floating Muslim village. &nbsp;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;After lunch, relax and buy souvenir for your friends and family from local people at <span style="color: #ff9900;">Muslim Village</span>.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Leave <span style="color: #ff9900;">Panyee Island</span> to the mainland. Visit <span style="color: #ff9900;">Suwankuha Temple</span>.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nb