(185, 'en', 'Package 3days 2nights Phuket City Tour – Phi Phi – Khai Island – Phang nga bay', 'package-3days-2nights-phuket-city-tour-ndash-phi-phi-ndash-khai-island-ndash-phang-nga-bay', 'Package 3days 2nights Phuket City Tour – Phi Phi – Khai Island – Phang nga bay.', '<div>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="color: #ff9900;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: xx-large;">P</span>ackage 3 days 2 nights</span> Phuket City Tour &ndash; Phi Phi &ndash; Khai Island &ndash; Phang nga bay</span>.&nbsp;Travel at Phuket town for see the old building style chinoprotugish, view on Khaorang and worship venerable monk Champ at Chalong temple include bring you to travel on the island, diving at Phipi island, Khai island, and Phang-nga bay.</p>\n</div>', '<p><strong>Day1:</strong> Phuket Airport - Hotel&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Arrival to Phuket Airport and transfer to your hotel. (Flight recommend to arrive before 10.00 hrs)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Approx 14.00 hrs, Driver will pick&nbsp; you up at hotel lobby for Phuket City Tour<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Visit the <span style="color: #ff9900;">Sino Portuguese House</span> in Downtown of Phuket City<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Visit the hill top of Rang Hill where the scenic of Phuket Town.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Visit the largest and most famous temple of Phuket, Chalong Temple.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Visit the viewpoint of <span style="color: #ff9900;">Kata</span>, <span style="color: #ff9900;">Karon</span> before going to see the sunset at <span style="color: #ff9900;">Phomtep Camp.</span><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp;Transfer back to your hotel &nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Day1:</strong> Phi Phi &ndash; Khai Island by speedboat &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &n