(159, 'en', 'Khao sok 3 Day 2 Nights (Included over night in the jungle camping)', 'khao-sok-3-day-2-nights-included-over-night-in-the-jungle-camping', 'Trekking to see the park.Enjoyment with many activity.You will get new experiences with sleep overnight in tent.', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color: #ff9900;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: xx-large;">W</span>hether</span> you are on armchair</span> explorer vicariously visiting Khao Sok or a rugged adventure about to embark on a trek traversing the park'' s uncharted terrain, you are about to enter part of the oldest and richest terrestrial ecosystem on Earth.</p>', '<table border="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; text-align: center;" colspan="2"><center>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: x-large; color: #000000;">Day 1</span></p>\n</center></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; width: 100px;">\n<p>07.00 AM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Hotel pick up from all around<span style="color: #ff9900;"> Phuket</span>, <span style="color: #ff9900;">Khao Lak</span>, <span style="color: #ff9900;">Krabi</span> and <span style="color: #ff9900;">Suratthani</span> for transfer to <span style="color: #ff9900;">Khao Sok</span> National Park.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>10.30 AM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Meet our friendly <span style="color: #ff9900;">Elephant</span> at the Jungle camp also your chance to be close and take a photos with them after that you will exiting by riding them to the real Jungle along the stream to visit nice waterfall is your chance to take a swim at nice pool of <span style="color: #ff9900;">waterfall</span>, after that you will riding Elephant again back to the Elephant camp and feeds them foods.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>12.30 PM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Lunch at our River side restaurant we offer kind of Thai delicious food are provide with cool water.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>02.00 PM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Enjoy with <span style="color: #ff9900;">Jungle River Canoe</span> along the river called <span style="color: #ff9900;">Sok River</span> take about 1:30 Hrs. is really relaxing trip are possibilities to see many kind of wild life animals for the example Monkeys, Birds, Snakes, Lizards and nice limestone mountain Cliff beside the river.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>04.00 PM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Check in to <span style="color: #ff9900;">Khao Sok River Lodge</span> locate is near by <span style="color: #ff9900;">Sok River</span> here is the best bungalow around of the National Park with many facilities are provide.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>07.00 PM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Dinner at Khao Sok River Lodge restaurant enjoy with Thai food.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99; text-align: center;" colspan="2"><center>\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: x-large; color: #000000;">Day 2</span></p>\n</center></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>08.00 AM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Breakfast at Khao Sok River Lodge. And prepare your self to visit National park by trekking.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>09.00 AM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Begin trekking to visit<span style="color: #ff9900;"> Khao Sok</span> National Park with our professional guide they will take good care and inform about the Park and all kind of plants, animals along the trek.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>12.00 PM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Take a swim at the nice waterfall in the Jungle and have lunch with Jungle style.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>01.00 PM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Further trekking to see some more <span style="color: #ff9900;">plants</span> and <span style="color: #ff9900;">animals</span>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>03.00 PM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Prepare tents to stay over night and rest till dinner time.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>07.00 PM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Dinner with Jungle style and over night in tents on this nights you will enjoy with nature sound for the example Birds, Frogs ext.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="background-color: #ffffcc;">\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;" colspan="2">\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;">Day 3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>08.00 AM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Breakfast in the Jungle and see morning life of animals.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>09.00 AM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Prepare to get back to<span style="color: #ff9900;"> Khao Sok River Lodge</span>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>10.00 AM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Depart to Khao Sok River Lodge.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>12.00 PM</p>\n</td>\n<td style="border: 1px solid #ffff99;">\n<p>Lunch with Thai set menu food at<span style="color: #ff9900;"> Khao Sok</span> restaurant and take a rest.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 